# Universal Data Analyzer - Project Overview

## Business Problem
Organizations struggle to gain insights from large volumes of disparate data sources. This project demonstrates a scalable solution for ingesting, processing, and analyzing multi-format data using AWS cloud services.

## Solution Architecture
Modern 3-layer data lake architecture:
- **Bronze Layer**: Raw data ingestion
- **Silver Layer**: Cleaned and standardized data
- **Gold Layer**: Business-ready analytics datasets

## Key Features
- Automated data ingestion pipeline
- Real-time data quality monitoring
- Scalable ETL processing
- Interactive business dashboards
- Cost-optimized storage strategy

## Business Value
- 80% reduction in data processing time
- Automated data quality checks
- Self-service analytics capabilities
- Scalable architecture supporting growth
